headline: Prediction: 3 Stocks That'll Be Worth More Than Costco 10 Years From Now
summary: It's not an easy matter to make predictions about the stock market, since no one really knows what it will do from day to day or even year to year.  First off, why am I focusing on Costco?  Costco's forward-looking price-to-earnings (P/E) ratio, for example, was recently 50, well above its five-year average of 39.
